# Directus data + strict typing

## Where data is fetched
- Prefer data fetching in +page.server.ts / +layout.server.ts.
- Use the shared Directus client from: src/lib/infrastructure/directus/

## Typing philosophy
- Do NOT type pages with full Directus collection types by default.
- Define types per query based on "fields" actually requested (partial/narrow payloads).
- Convert Directus payloads into domain/view models before components render.

## Boundary safety
- Treat Directus responses as unknown until validated.
- Use Zod schemas matching the exact fields requested.
- Keep mapping functions centralized (domain/data layer), not in Svelte components.

## Submodule types
- $cms types are reference/base schemas only. Do not modify submodule.
- App should own request/result types derived from queries.
